## Web API Endpoints (HTTP, not SNMP)

| Action | Method | URL |
|--------|--------|-----|
| Login | POST | http://{host}/goform/login |
| Rename ONU | POST | http://{host}/goform/setOnu |
| Reboot ONU | POST | http://{host}/goform/setOnu |

### Login form params
```
user={u}&pass={p}&username={u}&password={p}&submit=Login
Authorization: Basic base64(user:pass)
```

### Rename ONU form params
```
onuId={web_id}&onuName={name}&onuOperation=modifyOnu
```

### Reboot ONU form params
```
onuId={web_id}&onuName=rebooter&onuOperation=rebootOp
```